    Song(id = 551,"011","","A twalisiwe",""," A twalisiwe - aleluia á<br> Nkulukumba bava - a twalisiwe nkulukumba<br> Hosi ya matilo wa ntamu Hinkwawo …<br> Hina ha ku dzunisa hina ha ku tlhangela …<br> Hina ha ku gandzela, hina ha ku twalisa …<br><br> Hina ka ku khensa, hi ku kwetsima …<br> Ka wena lo kukulu, ku kuku swinwene …<br> Hosi yesu Kriste, nwana wa Xikwembu …<br> Wena xinyenpfana, xa nkulukumba bava …<br><br> Wena U susaka, swidjoho swa misava …<br> Hi twela wusiwana, U va U yamukela …<br> Swikhongelo Swa hina<br> Hi twele wusiwana, hi tipswalo ta wena.<br><br> A twalisiwe nkulukumba baba<br> Hi wena wo kwetsima hi wena unga Hosi<br> Hi wena unga henlha, Hosi Yesu Kriste …<br> Ni moya wo kwetsima, a nfunwini wa bava. <br>"),

